HEADWORD: Manchu
<hw>Man*chu"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Written also
<ets>Manchoo</ets>, <ets>Mantchoo</ets>, etc.]</ety> <def>Of or
pertaining to Manchuria or its inhabitants.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos>
<def>A native or inhabitant of Manchuria; also, the language spoken by
the Manchus.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

